VALUES
  ('dietitian-moex-04404', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於維生素參與代謝的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["Transketolase的活性可以用於評估維生素B 之營養狀況 1", "維生素B 參與glutathione peroxidase與glutathione reductase的反應，故對紅血球有抗氧化及保護之作 2 用", "Pyruvate carboxylase需要biotin作為輔因子", "Niacin缺乏與乳酸症的發生有關"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "67543ae9d102", "answer_pdf_sha1": "59e7cd37c769", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04405', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '於糖解作用中，常見何種酵素之缺陷可能會導致紅血球之溶血性貧血？', '["六碳糖激酶（hexokinase）", "葡萄糖-6-磷酸激酶（glucose-6-phosphate kinase）", "磷酸果糖激酶（phosphofructose kinase）", "丙酮酸激酶（pyruvate kinase）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "67543ae9d102", "answer_pdf_sha1": "59e7cd37c769", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
